EKIPIZZA S01E24: NBA
Pogledajte novu epizodu Mozzartove serije

04 Nov 2019

Momci sede u Mozzart kladionici, duboko zagledani u liste i prognoze za novu NBA sezonu. Svako ima svog favorita za novog osvajača prstena, pa nije lako doći do zajedničkog tiketa...

EXAMPLE S01E24: NBA
Check out a new episode of the Mozzart series

04 Nov 2019

The guys are sitting in a Mozzart bookmaker, looking deeply at the rosters and forecasts for the new NBA season. Everyone has their favorite for the new ring winner, so it's not easy to get to a common ticket ...
